title: Pats- Jets Recap; TNF Preview, Eagles Talk with Bo Wulf
itunes:title: Pats- Jets Recap; TNF Preview, Eagles Talk with Bo Wulf
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, and Gregg Rosenthal recap the painful Patriots- Jets matchup (3:24) but not before breaking down a beach boys feud. The heroes preview the TNF matchup between the Colts and the Titans (18:15) and Bo Wulf joins to talk about the Eagles and more specifically if Carson Wentz is declining (25:55) The heroes wrap out the show with answering some mailbag questions (36:15).
